+----------------------+
|  How to add a theme  |
+----------------------+

-) In "rdpproxy.ini" config file in CFG_PATH, add the name of the theme <theme_name>
   as value of key "load_theme" in "internal_mod" subsection :

/*************************************
[internal_mod]
load_theme=<theme_name>
*************************************/

-) In "themes" directory in CFG_PATH,
   create a subdirectory with the name of the theme <theme_name>
-) In this <theme_name> subdirectory:
      .) Add a logo image file named "logo.png" or "logo.bmp"
         CFG_PATH/themes/<theme_name>/logo.(png or bmp)
      .) Add a "theme.ini" file with the following structure :
         CFG_PATH/themes/<theme_name>/theme.ini

/*************************************
[global]
bgcolor=0xDD8015
# bgcolor=ORANGE
fgcolor=WHITE
separator_color=BROWN
focus_color=DARK_RED
error_color=RED
logo=yes

[edit]
bgcolor=WHITE
fgcolor=BLACK
focus_color=DARK_RED


[tooltip]
bgcolor=PALE_BLUE
fgcolor=DARK_BLUE
border_color=DARK_GREEN

[selector]
line1_bgcolor=PALE_ORANGE
line1_fgcolor=BLACK
line2_bgcolor=LIGHT_ORANGE
line2_fgcolor=BLACK
selected_bgcolor=MEDIUM_RED
selected_fgcolor=WHITE
focus_bgcolor=DARK_RED
focus_fgcolor=WHITE
label_bgcolor=MEDIUM_RED
label_fgcolor=WHITE
*************************************/

Note:
Values are examples, those are some predefined colors.
Color values can be defined as RGB color in hexadecimal (with 0x prefix).
"logo" key in "global" section indicate if the "logo.png" or "logo.bmp"
image file is used or ignored.

 Predefined Colors :
 +-----------------------+----------+
 |  BLACK                | 0x000000 |
 +-----------------------+----------+
 |  GREY                 | 0xc0c0c0 |
 +-----------------------+----------+
 |  MEDIUMGREY           | 0xa0a0a0 |
 +-----------------------+----------+
 |  DARK_GREY            | 0x8c8a8c |
 +-----------------------+----------+
 |  ANTHRACITE           | 0x808080 |
 +-----------------------+----------+
 |  WHITE                | 0xffffff |
 +-----------------------+----------+

 +-----------------------+----------+
 |  BLUE                 | 0x0000ff |
 +-----------------------+----------+
 |  DARK_BLUE            | 0x00007f |
 +-----------------------+----------+
 |  CYAN                 | 0x00ffff |
 +-----------------------+----------+
 |  DARK_BLUE_WIN        | 0x002060 |
 +-----------------------+----------+
 |  DARK_BLUE_BIS        | 0x081f60 |
 +-----------------------+----------+
